text:
Tuna, red shrimp, flounder, squid... Is this yellowtail?
It's amazing...!

Hehe~
we got lots of sashimi!

Oh, so when Kiriko was fanning,
she was cooling the sushi rice?

Hehe...
I also... grated the wasabi...

They even have pickled radish,
daikon sprouts, and natto...

Yeah, the greengrocer in the shopping street gave them
as a thank-you for helping at the fish market!

Alright, everyone, take a seat!
Let's eat to our heart's content~!

Hehe, thank you for the meal...
Thank you, Kogane-chan...
